Alright.

00:17:45.000 --> 00:17:51.000
As we're waiting and refreshing the page, what is your favorite thing that you wrote about on your secret, secret blog?

00:17:51.000 --> 00:17:53.000
Oh, my secret, secret blog.

00:17:53.000 --> 00:17:55.000
It's got to be gardening.

00:17:55.000 --> 00:17:57.000
So my partner and I, we garden at home.

00:17:57.000 --> 00:18:00.000
And it's been really nice to sort of engage with the environment.

00:18:00.000 --> 00:18:02.000
And start to grow our own food.

00:18:02.000 --> 00:18:06.000
And it's been incredible to see just the amount of things that we've been able to make.

00:18:06.000 --> 00:18:10.000
And it's only by sort of looking back at it that it sort of like really hits home.

00:18:17.000 --> 00:18:18.000
Yeah.

00:18:20.000 --> 00:18:21.000
This is not a question.

00:18:21.000 --> 00:18:24.000
I just really want to acknowledge how amazing you are.

00:18:24.000 --> 00:18:26.000
Truly, you brought tears to my eyes.

00:18:26.000 --> 00:18:28.000
So thank you for sharing.

00:18:28.000 --> 00:18:31.000
And truly, it's amazing that you did all that you did.

00:18:32.000 --> 00:18:35.000
Because that is not easy on so many levels.

00:18:35.000 --> 00:18:36.000
So I can completely relate.

00:18:36.000 --> 00:18:37.000
So really, truly, thank you.

00:18:37.000 --> 00:18:38.000
Thank you.

